# Bug Museum — ignore build artifacts. Students build these themselves.
# Tracked on purpose: source (*.c/*.h), notes (*.md), and the curated study
# artifacts (asm_*.txt, dec_*.c). Everything compiled is ignored below.

# Variant runnable executables (root build.ps1 -Exe) -> <variant>/bin/
**/bin/

# Capstone "Cascade" build output (stack-overflow/capstone/build.ps1) -> build/<config>/
stack-overflow/capstone/build/

# Withheld capstone answer key + trigger harnesses — must never ship.
# (Also covered by stack-overflow/capstone/.gitignore; repeated here as a backstop.)
stack-overflow/capstone/_solution/

# Compiled outputs anywhere (belt-and-suspenders for in-place builds)
*.obj
*.exe
*.dll
*.lib
*.exp
*.ilk
*.pdb

# Editor / OS noise
.vs/
*.user
Thumbs.db
